<p>If you want to report problems or suggest new features, use the <a href="https://github.com/terroo/terminal-finances/issues">issues</a> of <a href="https://github.com/terroo/terminal-finances/">GitHub</a></p>

<p>The official page of <a href="https://github.com/terroo/terminal-finances/">Terminal Finances</a> is: <a href="https://github.com/terroo/terminal-finances">https://github.com/terroo/terminal-finances</a></p>

<p>If you want to uninstall</p>
<ul>
  <li>Compiled version</li>
</ul>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">git clone https://github.com/terroo/terminal-finances
<span class="nb">cd </span>terminal-finances
<span class="nb">sudo </span>make uninstall</code></pre></figure>

<ul>
  <li>In Windows, access the Control Panel and go to Add/Remove Programming, right-click on Terminal Finances and choose: Uninstall.</li>
  <li>If you used <a href="https://github.com/terroo/app-get">app-get</a> on Linux, just run the command:</li>
</ul>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">app-get <span class="nt">--remove</span> terminal-finances</code></pre></figure>

<p>Thanks!</p>

